org.libav.avcodec

Interface IFrameWrapper

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IWrapper
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractFrameWrapper, FrameWrapper53, FrameWrapper54

    public interface IFrameWrapper
extends IWrapper
    Wrapper for the AVFrame. It provides access to some of the AVFrame properties.
    Author:
    Ondrej Perutka
